Donald L. Runkle, MBA

Age : 71Public asset : 560,364 USDLinked companies :  Lear Corporation 





Summary 



Mr. Donald L. Runkle is Executive Chairman at Ioxus, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Transonic Combustion, Inc., Lear Corp., Environmental Systems Products, Inc., Envirotest Systems Holdings Corp., Lean Enterprise Institute, Inc., Massachusetts Institute of Technology, VIA Motors, Inc. and WinCup, Inc. Mr. Runkle was previously employed as Executive Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by EcoMotors, Inc., Chairman by EP Management Corp., Vice Chairman & Chief Technology Officer by Delphi Corp. /Old/, Vice President by Delphi Automotive Systems Corp., General Manager by Delphi Energy & Engine Management Systems (UK) Overseas Corp, VP, GM-Energy & Engine Management Systems by General Motors Corp., Chairman by Autocam Corp., Chairman by EaglePicher Corp., and Vice Chairman by Ford Motor Co.He also served on the board at Asia Automotive Acquisition Corp. and Federal National Mortgage Association.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan, a graduate degree from the University of Michigan and a graduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.



